<span id="Introduction"></span>
== Einleitung ==

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
[[Image:Movie_Workbench_icon.svg|24px]] [[Movie_Workbench|Movie]] is an [https://www.freecad.org/addons.php external workbench] to animate cameras and objects, and to record and play videos.
</div>

