<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
== Installation ==
</div>

<div lang="en" dir="ltr" class="mw-content-ltr">
The [[Movie_Workbench|Movie Workbench]] is available through the [[Std_AddonMgr|Addon Manager]]. Any Movie 3rd party dependencies should be managed automatically through the Addon Manager.
</div> 

